        "created_at": "2025-03-31T15:42:17.208Z",
        "cooked": "<p>There are multiple support threads that are solved by having the user input the correct PIN/password (Signal vs device unlocking). I suggest that the Signal PIN be renamed to something that is not so easily confused with the device PIN. “Signal recovery code” is one suggestion. I don’t really like it, but I like stating problems without proposing solutions even less.</p>",
