        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"CueHD\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"68154\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/cuehd/48/42510_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> CueHD:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“Signal recovery code”</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Not to mess up with “Backup pass phrase”.<br>\nI know local backup is something completly different but in my point of view it would make things less confusing if things will get harmonized.</p>",
